author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I’m protecting the shower tray with Builder Board Hydro Shield. This is 18 mils thick and waterproof. If I drop anything it won’t damage the tray and the surface cleans up nicely. This is definitely a great option for protecting showers and tile floors. Many thanks to Surface Shields for sponsoring this video 🔥
title: Shower Tray Protection Tips - #shorts #bathroomremodel #sponsored
